Tessers-d idmaren-is fell-i, qrib yedda laɛmer-iw.
Yessers-d ifassen-is ɣef yedmaren-iw, qrib yedda laɛmer-iw.
Cewḍeɣ, bɣiɣ ad gneɣ yid-m.
Cewḍeɣ, bɣiɣ ad gneɣ yid-k.
Urgaɣ ṭfeɣ-kem seg idmaren dɣa ḥusseɣ yemmar-d kullec deg upijama-w.
Tefkiḍ-iyi axessaṛ s tqendurt-nni telsiḍ.
Rwaḥ a laɛmer-iw ad ngen yiwen yiḍ lwaḥid.
Rwaḥ a laɛmer-iw ad ngen yiwen yiḍ jmiɛ.
Yezga yekcem ɣur-s s axxam.
Tezga tessawal-as-d ad yekcem ɣur-s ɣer axxam.
Gneɣ yid-s snat n tikal ur teṛwa ara.
Gneɣ yid-s snat n tikal ur yerwa ara.
Tugi tmeṭṭut-is ad as-tefk ayen yebɣa.
